# .github/CODEOWNERS
# =============================================================================
# Aerealith AI CODEOWNERS
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Default review ownership for the Aerealith AI Nx monorepo.
#
# Owner format:
#   <path-pattern> <owner> <owner> <owner>
#
# Examples:
#   /apps/frontend/ @sinless777 @SinLess-Games/frontend
#   /.github/       @sinless777 @SinLess-Games/maintainers
#
# Notes:
# - Each rule is a path pattern followed by one or more owners.
# - Owners can be users or GitHub teams.
# - GitHub team owners must be visible and have write access to the repository.
# - Later matching rules override earlier matching rules.
# - Keep this aligned with .github/assignees.yaml and repo-management rules.
# =============================================================================

